            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#35618c] via-[#295781] to-[#1d4060]"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.07]">
              <div class="absolute bottom-20 right-20 w-96 h-96 bg-[#d0e4ff] rounded-full blur-3xl hero-float"></div>
              <div class="absolute top-10 left-40 w-48 h-48 bg-[#a2cdfe] rounded-full blur-3xl hero-float-delay"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center relative z-10 w-full">
              <div class="space-y-6 hero-content">
                <span
                  class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/15 backdrop-blur-md rounded-full text-xs font-bold text-[#d0e4ff] tracking-widest uppercase border border-white/10">💬
                  Kết nối an toàn</span>
                <h1 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-[3.5rem] font-black text-white leading-[1.1] tracking-tight">
                  Đăng tin miễn phí –<br /><span class="text-[#a2cdfe]">Bán nhanh trong 1 ngày</span>
